场 141 次，打入 8 球，送出 4 次助攻，他帮助葡萄牙夺得了 2016 年欧洲杯冠军，此外，他还帮助葡萄牙队在 2019 年夺得了首届欧国联冠军。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9b6883bd07222797c01a18bfa2333a44_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "80 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/663795011"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I18fe/7zB56I1EAMaCTEwOTc4NzY4MyCJydO1BjAAOBdAD3IJNjYzNzk1MDExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1723171172.388187", "card_id": "Q_20733826", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 916}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "怎样提高说话时的瞬时反应能力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "很多时候，在事后懊恼：如果当时能够这么说就好了！因为自己当时脑子转得不够快或者没有准备，导致真相被隐瞒，这是很痛苦的一件事..."}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-f554283a451267e35340f2305eb2d5f9_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/20733826"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0I18fe/7zB56I1EAMaBjQ3NDAxNCCXwPiHBTAAOOiOBEAQcggyMDczMzgyNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1723171172.389086", "card_id": "Q_663405504", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在《绝区零》中你明白了哪些知识后，体验开始直线上升？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "作为一款需要一定操作的游戏，很奇怪在知乎还没有出现这个系列的问题，但作为操作小白，特别是从星铁转过来的玩家，真的很需要这个问题的答案，还望各位大佬不吝赐